items.caption_text:
I give you an ode to my internet friends—who don't know we're friends—but who inspire me weekly. Individually and collectively, they remind me of my north star and my ultimate dream of a self-sufficient life...

Read more ➡️ livingbetterwithless.substack.com
(link also in bio)

@martijndoolaard - A masterclass in stillness and intention in the Italian Alps.
@wildshegoes91 - Traveler, adventurer, and rambler after my own heart.
@roamingwildrosie - Solo-hiker leaves London to renovate an old cabin in Sweden, yes, please!
@girlinthewoodz - "Don't forget to get outside and get happy"
@hannahleeduggan - Ah, to live alone in the woods, build, dance and travel. 
@projectkamp - Prototyping a sustainable and communial way of living. 
@flockfingerlakes - Three friends buy land together with the aim of regenerative living and working communally.

